{"tid":1334743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[721] 踢波打前鋒嘅要做好心理準備應對製煙機","createTime":"2019-07-20T08:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T08:44:47.000Z","uid":59965,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b41f94d15e04bde0cc49dafb59a5b99df99c1d48","tid":1334743,"uid":59965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:27:20.000Z","msg":"見到有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打開左po話有狗借走左製煙機<br />\n絕對有理由相信班狗想放煙打人<br />\n<br />\n當然<br />\n如果呢件事無發生係最好<br />\n<br />\n但希望聽日企得係前線嘅手足做好準備先<br />\n<br />\n裝備：空水樽製品，浮板製品，行山杖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外就係非勇武請做一樣野 就係保護身邊嘅手足唔好比狗拖走<br />\n萬一真係拖走左 後果大家應該都知<br />\n<br />\n所以千萬不要落單<br />\n不要戀戰<br />\nbe water<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eca0c6ccbc6f1fa130166064f6280ab3055ab3f","tid":1334743,"uid":59965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5921f0f4a0c052e274d35a902c189e3dd96eaf5c","tid":1334743,"uid":59965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7dffe455eae90838f4d18d103c6ae4b5dacca69","tid":1334743,"uid":59965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce644ae23e181389181a517b0bb5e54637a293af","tid":1334743,"uid":59965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31db59cf76540ddac02c5e8c795e725d7e8534a1","tid":1334743,"uid":59965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"h